{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Plateforme Microservices - Université",
    "description": "Collection complète pour tester la plateforme de publications universitaire.\n\n## Architecture\n- **API Gateway** → http://localhost:8080 (point d'entrée unique)\n- **Publication Service** → http://localhost:8081 (direct)\n- **Recherche Service** → http://localhost:8082 (direct)\n- **Administration Service** → http://localhost:8083 (direct)\n- **Eureka Server** → http://localhost:8761\n\n## Authentification\nLe Gateway est en mode DEV : sans token Bearer, il injecte automatiquement un utilisateur test (ETUDIANT). Pour simuler un ADMIN, utiliser la variable `admin_token`.\n\n## Ordre de test recommandé\n1. Health Checks\n2. Publications (CRUD)\n3. Recherche\n4. Administration (modération)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "gateway_url",   "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "pub_url",       "value": "http://localhost:8081", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "search_url",    "value": "http://localhost:8082", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "admin_url",     "value": "http://localhost:8083", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "eureka_url",    "value": "http://localhost:8761", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "publication_id","value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Rempli automatiquement par le test de création" },
    { "key": "jwt_token",     "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Token JWT Bearer (optionnel en mode DEV)" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🏥 Health Checks",
      "description": "Vérification de l'état de tous les services de l'infrastructure.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Eureka Server - Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{eureka_url}}", "host": ["{{eureka_url}}"] },
            "description": "Dashboard Eureka — liste les services enregistrés."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "API Gateway - Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/actuator/health", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["actuator","health"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "API Gateway - Routes enregistrées",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/actuator/gateway/routes", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["actuator","gateway","routes"] },
            "description": "Liste les routes configurées dans le Gateway (publication, recherche, admin)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Publication Service - Health (direct)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{pub_url}}/actuator/health", "host": ["{{pub_url}}"], "path": ["actuator","health"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Recherche Service - Health (direct)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{search_url}}/actuator/health", "host": ["{{search_url}}"], "path": ["actuator","health"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Administration Service - Health (direct)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{admin_url}}/actuator/health", "host": ["{{admin_url}}"], "path": ["actuator","health"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Elasticsearch - Cluster Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "http://localhost:9200/_cluster/health", "host": ["http://localhost:9200"], "path": ["_cluster","health"] },
            "description": "Vérifie l'état du cluster Elasticsearch (green/yellow/red)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "📄 Publications - Via Gateway",
      "description": "Toutes les requêtes passent par le Gateway (port 8080). En mode DEV, l'utilisateur test (ETUDIANT) est injecté automatiquement si aucun token n'est fourni.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Créer une publication (SERVICE)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.data && body.data.id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('publication_id', body.data.id);",
                  "        console.log('publication_id enregistré :', body.data.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Statut 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Statut initial EN_MODERATION', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.statut).to.eql('EN_MODERATION');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"SERVICE\",\n  \"titre\": \"Cours de mathématiques niveau Licence 1\",\n  \"description\": \"Propose des cours particuliers de mathématiques pour les étudiants en L1. Spécialité analyse et algèbre. Tarif négociable.\",\n  \"categorie\": \"Cours particuliers\",\n  \"localisation\": \"Dschang, Cameroun\",\n  \"medias\": [],\n  \"dateExpiration\": \"2026-12-31\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/api/v1/publications", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","publications"] },
            "description": "Crée une publication. Statut initial = EN_MODERATION. L'ID est sauvegardé dans la variable `publication_id`."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "Créer une publication (STAGE)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Statut 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Type STAGE', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.type).to.eql('STAGE');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"STAGE\",\n  \"titre\": \"Stage développeur web - Startup FinTech Douala\",\n  \"description\": \"Offre de stage de 3 mois dans une startup FinTech en pleine croissance. Stack : React, Spring Boot, PostgreSQL. Gratification selon profil.\",\n  \"categorie\": \"Informatique\",\n  \"localisation\": \"Douala, Cameroun\",\n  \"medias\": [],\n  \"dateExpiration\": \"2026-08-31\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/api/v1/publications", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","publications"] }
          },
          "response": []
